                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1721" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0271</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8713 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“盐”之有理——益盐堂之天下减盐篇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Salt”Makes Senses——Salt Reduction of Yi Yantang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋玉石，张红宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">益盐堂（应城）健康盐制盐有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">益盐堂公司；食用盐；全渠道营销模式；健康用盐中国行</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yi Yantang company;  Edible Salt; All channels’ Marketing Model; Health China go with Salt</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了益盐堂（应城）健康盐制盐有限公司总经理杨总，在面对食盐有可能发开的前提条件下，组织全体员工就另起炉灶还是继续推进与盐业公司合作的渠道和品牌模式两种观点展开了热烈讨论。大家经过对食盐行业进行深入调研的基础上，决定继续推进与盐业公司合作，为消费者提供更加完善优质的销售服务，以盐为基础研发和拓展与盐相关的调味及食品，增强商户满意度，利用公司的营销人才优势拓展社会经销商渠道，构建全渠道营销模式。同时，以“健康用盐中国行”公益活动为载体，向终端消费者传播益盐堂的品牌美誉，从而为应对未来挑战奠定良好基础。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Yi Yantang (Ying Cheng), an limited company of making healthy salt, (the following abbreviation will be Yi Yantang company) and Xiaogan Guangyan  Huayuan salt making co. LTD, both are affiliated with the new capital of Chengdu Huayuan chemical co., LTD. (002539). Yi Yantang’s products cover various high-end of more than 30 kinds of salts, and more than 20 kinds of products have gained green certification, which is the most perfect domestic product line with the strongest research and development ability. And it can sale 300000 tons of annual sales of high-end edible salt, and such high-end edible salt ranks first in the country. This case records when Yang faced with salt industry environment being likely to open, on the basis of in-depth research on the salt industry, he decided to continue to push forward the cooperation with salt company channels and modes of brand, provide consumers with high-quality sales service, accumulating corresponding guest and related distribution system and allocating system. On the basis of the salt, they will make a research and development salt flavor and food, strengthening the merchant’s satisfaction, using the company&#39;s marketing talent advantage to expand social dealer channels, building the whole channel marketing model. At the same time, they will make &quot;Health China with Salt&quot; public welfare activities as the carrier to spread the brand reputation of Yi Yantang to the end consumer, thus laying a good foundation to cope with the challenge of the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《企业家社会责任》、《品牌管理》、《零售管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST、SWOT及五力模型分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
